<li id="cite_note-jamisonbrereton-6"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-jamisonbrereton_6-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-jamisonbrereton_6-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-jamisonbrereton_6-2"><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text">Stephanie Jamison and Joel Brereton (2014), The Rigveda&#160;: the earliest religious poetry of India, Oxford University Press, <link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r951705291"/><a href="/wiki/ISBN_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="ISBN (identifier)">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/978-0199370184" title="Special:BookSources/978-0199370184">978-0199370184</a>, pp. 4, 7–9</span>
