<li id="cite_note-99"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-99">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">Chakrabarti, D.K. The Early Use of Iron in India (1992) <a href="/wiki/Oxford_University_Press" title="Oxford University Press">Oxford University Press</a> argues that it may refer to any metal. If ayas refers to iron, the Rigveda must date to the late second millennium at the earliest.</span>
